config SAMPLE_RUST_HELLO
	tristate "Hello Rust learning module"
	depends on RUST
	help
	  A simple hello world module for learning Rust kernel development.
	  Demonstrates module! macro, parameters, KVec, and pr_info!.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called hello_rust.

	  If unsure, say N.

config SAMPLE_RUST_CHARDEV
	tristate "Rust char device learning module"
	depends on RUST
	help
	  A character device module for learning Rust kernel development.
	  Demonstrates MiscDevice, ioctl, Mutex, and user-kernel data transfer.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called rust_chardev.

	  If unsure, say N.

config SAMPLE_RUST_SYNC
	tristate "Rust sync learning module"
	depends on RUST
	help
	  A misc-device sample that teaches shared state, blocking consumers,
	  ring buffers, and sync primitive trade-offs in Rust.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called rust_sync.

	  If unsure, say N.

config SAMPLE_RUST_WORKQUEUE
	tristate "Rust workqueue learning module"
	depends on RUST
	help
	  A misc-device sample that queues deferred work and exposes completion
	  counters through a small ioctl interface.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here:
	  the module will be called rust_workqueue.

	  If unsure, say N.

config SAMPLE_RUST_PROCFS
	tristate "Rust procfs learning module"
	depends on RUST
